---
title: Open-Faced Portobello Sandwiches with Roasted Bell Pepper and Fresh Mozzarella
description: Who says sandwiches are just for lunch? Crusty ciabatta is topped with sweet roasted yellow bell peppers, hearty portobellos, and fresh mozzarella, then baked until the cheese gets perfectly golden and gooey. A simple spinach salad on the side makes this a meal for any time of day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5703cf53f8b25ec2608b4567.jpg
